title: Austria Women Have Advanced in the EC
body_text:
Austria Women Have Advanced in the EC
The European Cup journey of the Women’s Football Bundesliga leader Austria Wien continues now.
The team of Stefan Kenesei prevailed on Wednesday in the second leg of the Women’s Europa Cup round of 16 at the Generali Arena against Anderlecht with a 2:1 victory and advanced to the last eight with an aggregate score of 3:1. There, Sparta Prague awaits on February 11/12 and 18/19, 2026. St. Pölten secured their first point in the Champions League with a 2:2 draw at Valerenga in the fourth match.
(APA/Red)
